<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <!-- Meta Data -->
  <%- include('partial/title.ejs'); %>

  <% if (data.NODE_ENV == 'production') { %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/production/css/about.min.css">
  <% } else { %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/fontawesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/responsive.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/select2.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/spacing.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/owl.carousel.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/bootstrap-datepicker.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/lib/css/magnific-popup.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/header.css">
  <% } %>

  <style>
    .about-page {
      padding: 60px 0;
      background: #f5f8ff;
    }

    .about-page h2 {
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #007bff;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .about-page h2::after {
      content: "";
      display: block;
      width: 80px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #007bff;
      margin: 10px auto 0 auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .term-heading {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: #004085;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }

    .term-heading::before {
      content: "\f06e"; /* FontAwesome icon for lock/privacy */
      font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free";
      font-weight: 900;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      color: #007bff;
    }

    .about-page p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #495057;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about-page ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .about-page ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #495057;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body onLoad="typeWriter()">
  <!-- Header -->
  <%- include('partial/header.ejs', { data: data }); %>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Start -->
  <div class="about-page pt_60 pb_30">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
          <p>Your privacy is critically important to us at QuickDoc. We are committed to protecting your personal
            information and ensuring transparency about how your data is used and stored.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">1. Information We Collect</h3>
          <p>We collect personal information such as your name, contact details, medical history, and appointment
            records. Non-personal data, like usage analytics, is also collected to improve our services.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">2. Use of Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>To provide and improve healthcare services.</li>
            <li>To communicate important updates and reminders.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="term-heading">3. Sharing of Information</h3>
          <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. Information may be shared with doctors, healthcare providers,
            or emergency services as necessary to provide the requested services.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">4. Data Security</h3>
          <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration,
            or disclosure. Access to sensitive information is restricted to authorized personnel only.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">5. Cookies & Tracking</h3>
          <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance user experience, track session data, and improve platform performance.
            Users can manage cookie preferences through their browser settings.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">6. User Rights</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Right to access personal data collected.</li>
            <li>Right to correct or update inaccurate information.</li>
            <li>Right to request deletion of personal data where applicable.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="term-heading">7. Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>We may use third-party services (e.g., analytics, payment processors). These services have their own
            privacy policies, and we ensure data sharing is secure and compliant.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">8. Changes to Privacy Policy</h3>
          <p>We may update this policy periodically. Continued use of the QuickDoc platform constitutes acceptance of
            the updated policy. Users are encouraged to review the policy regularly.</p>

          <h3 class="term-heading">9. Contact Us</h3>
          <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or your data, you can contact our support team at
            privacy@medbuddy.com or call us at +91-XXXXXXXXXX.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Privacy Policy End -->

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('partial/footer.ejs'); %>

  <script>
    var i = 0;
    var txt = 'WELCOME TO MEDBUDDY';
    var speed = 60;

    function typeWriter() {
      if (i < txt.length) {
        document.getElementById("typeit").innerHTML += txt.charAt(i);
        i++;
        setTimeout(typeWriter, speed);
      }
    }
  </script>

  <script defer src="assets/lib/js/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="assets/lib/js/popper.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="assets/lib/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="assets/lib/js/all.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="assets/lib/js/select2.full.min.js"></script>
  <script defer src="assets/js/about.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
